      <title>Hexo简易博客搭建教程</title>
      <link href="/posts/11093.html"/>
      <url>/posts/11093.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="基础搭建"><a href="#基础搭建" class="headerlink" title="基础搭建"></a>基础搭建</h1><h2 id="安装必要工具并搭建本地博客"><a href="#安装必要工具并搭建本地博客" class="headerlink" title="安装必要工具并搭建本地博客"></a>安装必要工具并搭建本地博客</h2><ul><li><p>git</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--检测是否成功安装git,若能正确显示版本号即表示成功安装</span><br><span class="line">git --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>node.js</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--检测是否成功安装node.js，若能正确显示版本号即表示成功安装</span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>hexo</p><ul><li>选择一个文件夹，把相关的博客信息存储到这个文件夹下,本人路径：&#x2F;Users&#x2F;clhao&#x2F;Blog</li></ul><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--安装hexo</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--hexo初始化配置</span><br><span class="line">hexo init</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--检测hexo是否安装完成</span><br><span class="line">hexo generate(hexo g)</span><br><span class="line">hexo server(hexo s)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/Hexo%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2.png" alt="Hexo初始化界面"></p></li><li><p>如上图所示，hexo本地博客就已经搭建完成，十分的简单～</p></li></ul><h2 id="将本地的博客部署到Github上"><a href="#将本地的博客部署到Github上" class="headerlink" title="将本地的博客部署到Github上"></a>将本地的博客部署到Github上</h2><ul><li><p>在github上创建项目代码库</p><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/github%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BA%93.png" alt="github创建项目库"></p></li><li><p>需要配置ssh密钥，配置完成之后才能将文件上传的github上(这一步比较关键)</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--新号配置ssh</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;你的邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/ssh%E5%AF%86%E9%92%A5%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE.png" alt="ssh密钥配置"></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--测试是否成功</span><br><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E5%88%B0github.png" alt="测试是否成功连接到github"></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--配置git个人信息</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;此处填你的用户名&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;此处填你的邮箱&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>获取github项目代码库的ssh路径</p><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96github%E5%BA%93ssh%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84.png" alt="获取github库ssh路径"></p></li><li><p>在.config.yml文件的最后更改以下代码</p><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/config.yml%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6ssh%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9.png" alt="config.yml文件ssh路径的修改"></p></li><li><p>最后，把本地的文件部署到github上</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--部署到git上</span><br><span class="line">hexo g -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="文章上传"><a href="#文章上传" class="headerlink" title="文章上传"></a>文章上传</h2><ul><li>文章的上传这个问题困扰了我挺久的，因为你不可能就只简单的做文字笔记，笔记里面肯定还有图片，如何把图片同步上传上去这是一个问题，但现在这个问题解决了。但是用的是Typora(之前用的是obsidian)，以后可能用云图床来代替。</li></ul><p>a) 在你本地的博客目录下，创造一个文件夹，用来存放文章的图片</p><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E5%AD%98%E6%94%BE%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95.png" alt="创建存放图片的目录"></p><p>b) 对全局图像进行设置（目的是每次放到Typora中的文件都同步复制到相应的路径下，就不用手动复制了，这里建议绝对路径)</p><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%85%A8%E5%B1%80%E5%9B%BE%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6.png" alt="全局图像复制"></p><p>c) 这篇文章的图片根目录，设置到你存放图片的目录下，注意要在source目录下</p><h2 id="域名设置"><a href="#域名设置" class="headerlink" title="域名设置"></a>域名设置</h2><p>【1】首先在阿里云上买一个域名(或者腾讯云，还能是一些其他的网站，那些比较便宜)</p><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0.png" alt="域名购买"></p><p>【2】在配置好自己域名的DNS解析</p><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%A5%BD%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D%E7%9A%84DNS.png" alt="设置好域名的DNS"></p><p>【3】再在source目录下创建一个CNAME文件，其中写入自己的域名</p><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/CNAME%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%86%99%E5%85%A5%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D.png" alt="CNAME文件中写入自己的域名"></p><p>【4】在github上写入自己的域名，然后就可以通过域名来访问自己的博客了</p><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/github%E4%B8%8A%E5%86%99%E5%85%A5%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D.png" alt="github上写入自己的域名"></p><ul><li>以上就是博客基础的步骤了，当然还是需要美化的～</li></ul><h1 id="主题和基础配置"><a href="#主题和基础配置" class="headerlink" title="主题和基础配置"></a>主题和基础配置</h1><ul><li>博客美化主要是用了Hexo官方的butterfly主题，可能会加点魔改(<a href="https://butterfly.js.org),但主要是满足日常记录文章的需要/">https://butterfly.js.org),但主要是满足日常记录文章的需要</a></li></ul><h2 id="安装butterfly主题"><a href="#安装butterfly主题" class="headerlink" title="安装butterfly主题"></a>安装butterfly主题</h2><ul><li><p>有多种安装方式，这里介绍git安装</p><ul><li><p>把butterfly主题clone下来</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-- 在hexo的根目录下</span><br><span class="line">git clone -b master https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly.git themes/butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>修改根目录下的.config.yml文件中的theme</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-- 注意:所有文件的修改都是要在冒号后面加个空格</span><br><span class="line">theme: butterfly</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>需要安装pub和stylus的渲染器</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p>把theme中的_config.yml文件中的内容复制出来放到根目录下，名字为_config.butterfly.yml。hexo会自动合并主题中的_config.yml和_config.butterfly.yml文件里面的配置，且_config.butterfly.yml优先级较高,这样butterfly已经安装完成了～</p><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%AE%8Cbutterfly%E4%B9%8B%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%E7%95%8C%E9%9D%A2.png" alt="安装完butterfly之后的界面"></p></li></ul><h2 id="常见配置"><a href="#常见配置" class="headerlink" title="常见配置"></a>常见配置</h2><h3 id="语言"><a href="#语言" class="headerlink" title="语言"></a>语言</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-- 支持英文，中文简体，中文繁体</span><br><span class="line">-- 修改根目录下的_config.yml文件</span><br><span class="line"># site</span><br><span class="line">title: 百木生</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: &#x27;追求心流&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">description: &#x27;愿有春风常盈袖，心中百木向阳生&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">keywords: 肥宅,技术宅,菜鸟,永恒的梦想者,不断前进</span><br><span class="line">author: chenlihao</span><br><span class="line">language: zh-CN</span><br><span class="line">timezone: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">email: cfrankm2022@outlook.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE.png" alt="语言配置"></p><h3 id="导航菜单"><a href="#导航菜单" class="headerlink" title="导航菜单"></a>导航菜单</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--修改_config.butterfly.yml文件</span><br><span class="line">--语法解释：|| 的左边是路径，右边是图标</span><br><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  主页: / || fas fa-home</span><br><span class="line">  档案: /archives/ || fas fa-archive</span><br><span class="line">  标签: /tags/ || fas fa-tags</span><br><span class="line">  分类: /categories/ || fas fa-folder-open</span><br><span class="line">  列表||fas fa-list:</span><br><span class="line">    音乐: /music/ || fas fa-music</span><br><span class="line">    电影: /movies/ || fas fa-video</span><br><span class="line">  链接: /link/ || fas fa-link</span><br><span class="line">  关于: /about/ || fas fa-heart</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  ——具体后面的图标可以在这个网站里面查找：https://fontawesome.com/v4/icons/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%AF%BC%E8%88%AA%E6%A0%8F%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%9B%BE.png" alt="导航栏效果图"></p><h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--修改_config.butterfly.yml文件</span><br><span class="line">highlight_theme: mac # 主题</span><br><span class="line">highlight_copy: true # 是否支持代码复制</span><br><span class="line">highlight_lang: true # show the code language</span><br><span class="line">highlight_shrink: false # 支持代码折叠</span><br><span class="line">highlight_height_limit: false # unit: px</span><br><span class="line">code_word_wrap: true #支持代码换行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%9B%BE.png" alt="代码显示效果图"></p><h3 id="创建标签页"><a href="#创建标签页" class="headerlink" title="创建标签页"></a>创建标签页</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--在hexo的根目录</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page tags</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--之后就可以找到source/tags/index.md这个文件</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--修改这个文件</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分類</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018-01-05 00:00:00</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%9B%BE.png" alt="标签效果图"></p><h3 id="创建分类页"><a href="#创建分类页" class="headerlink" title="创建分类页"></a>创建分类页</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--在hexo的根目录</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--之后就可以找到source/categories/index.md这个文件</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--修改这个文件</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分類</span><br><span class="line">date: 2018-01-05 00:00:00</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/imgs/Hexo%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C%E5%9B%BE.png" alt="分类效果图"></p><h3 id="文章上传相关设置"><a href="#文章上传相关设置" class="headerlink" title="文章上传相关设置"></a>文章上传相关设置</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 可以将上传的文章进行分类</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Hexo简易博客搭建教程</span><br><span class="line">tag: 学习</span><br><span class="line">category: </span><br><span class="line">- 环境搭建</span><br><span class="line">- 博客搭建</span><br><span class="line">typora-root-url: ../../../Blog/source</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#设置文章的封面图片</span><br><span class="line">cover: 图片地址</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="配置文章链接数字转字母"><a href="#配置文章链接数字转字母" class="headerlink" title="配置文章链接数字转字母"></a>配置文章链接数字转字母</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--相应的参考路径:https://github.com/rozbo/hexo-abbrlink</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-abbrlink --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--后缀配置成.html,在hexo根目录下的 \<span class="emphasis">_config.yml 文件下</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">permalink: post/:abbrlink.html</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="本地搜索功能"><a href="#本地搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="本地搜索功能"></a>本地搜索功能</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--相应的参考路径:https://github.com/wzpan/hexo-generator-search</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--在_config.yml文件末尾添加</span><br><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  path: search.xml</span><br><span class="line">  field: all</span><br><span class="line">  content: true</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">--在_config.butterfly.yml文件中把local_search的使能打开</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Butterfly侧边栏修改"><a href="#Butterfly侧边栏修改" class="headerlink" title="Butterfly侧边栏修改"></a>Butterfly侧边栏修改</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--在_config.butterfly.yml文件中搜索aside</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#修改公告内容</span><br><span class="line">card_announcement:</span><br><span class="line"> enable: true</span><br><span class="line"> content: 桃花流水窅然去，别有天地非人间</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="博客美化"><a href="#博客美化" class="headerlink" title="博客美化"></a>博客美化</h1><h2 id="Live2D看板娘插件"><a href="#Live2D看板娘插件" class="headerlink" title="Live2D看板娘插件"></a>Live2D看板娘插件</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--在_config.yml文件下加入一下配置信息</span><br><span class="line">live2d:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true #看板娘使能</span><br><span class="line">  scriptFrom: local </span><br><span class="line">  tagMode: false # 标签模式, 是否仅替换 live2d tag标签而非插入到所有页面中</span><br><span class="line">  debug: false # 调试, 是否在控制台输出日志</span><br><span class="line">  model:</span><br><span class="line">    use: live2d-widget-model-hibiki # npm-module package name</span><br><span class="line">  display:</span><br><span class="line">    position: left #控制看板娘位置</span><br><span class="line">    width: 150 #控制看板娘大小</span><br><span class="line">    height: 300 #控制看板娘大小</span><br><span class="line">  mobile:</span><br><span class="line">    show: false # 手机中是否展示</span><br><span class="line">--安装live2d和模型</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-helper-live2d</span><br><span class="line">npm install --save live2d-widget-model-hibiki</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="追番页面设置"><a href="#追番页面设置" class="headerlink" title="追番页面设置"></a>追番页面设置</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--安装追番的插件</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-bilibili-bangumi --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--在_config.yml文件中加入这几行，其中vmid是自己的b站id</span><br><span class="line">bangumi: # 追番设置</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  path:</span><br><span class="line">  vmid: 385200033</span><br><span class="line">  title: &#x27;追番列表&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  quote: &#x27;我从未离开过这里&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">  show: 1</span><br><span class="line">  lazyload: false</span><br><span class="line">  loading:</span><br><span class="line">  metaColor:</span><br><span class="line">  color:</span><br><span class="line">  webp:</span><br><span class="line">  progress:</span><br><span class="line">  extra_options:</span><br><span class="line">    key: value</span><br><span class="line">--同时打开主题的懒加载_config.butterfly.yml</span><br><span class="line">lazyload: true</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--执行完hexo g 和hexo s 之后，再去更新一下自己的番剧列表</span><br><span class="line">hexo bangumi -u #番</span><br><span class="line">hexo cinema -u #剧</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--删除自己番剧列表的数据</span><br><span class="line">hexo bangumi -d #番</span><br><span class="line">hexo cinema -d #剧</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="相关图像配置"><a href="#相关图像配置" class="headerlink" title="相关图像配置"></a>相关图像配置</h2><ul><li>一图流：在source目录下创建文件夹css，并添加文件custom.css,并添加以下内容</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/*top-img黑色透明玻璃效果移除，不建议加，除非你执着于完全一图流或者背景图对比色明显 */</span><br><span class="line">#page-header:not(.not-top-img):before &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background-color: transparent !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/* 首页文章卡片 */</span><br><span class="line">#recent-posts &gt; .recent-post-item &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/* 首页侧栏卡片 */</span><br><span class="line">#aside-content .card-widget &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/* 文章页面正文背景 */</span><br><span class="line">div#post &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/* 分页页面 */</span><br><span class="line">div#page &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/* 归档页面 */</span><br><span class="line">div#archive &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/* 标签页面 */</span><br><span class="line">div#tag &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/* 分类页面 */</span><br><span class="line">div#category &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/*夜间模式伪类遮罩层透明*/</span><br><span class="line">[data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;] #recent-posts &gt; .recent-post-item &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: #121212;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;] .card-widget &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: #121212 !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;] div#post &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: #121212 !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;] div#tag &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: #121212 !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;] div#archive &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: #121212 !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;] div#page &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: #121212 !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;] div#category &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: #121212 !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[data-theme=&quot;dark&quot;] div#category &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: transparent !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">/* 页脚透明 */</span><br><span class="line">#footer &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: transparent !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/* 头图透明 */</span><br><span class="line">#page-header &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  background: transparent !important;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#rightside &gt; div &gt; button &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  border-radius: 5px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--相关图像修改</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#网页背景图片</span><br><span class="line">在_config.butterfly.yml文件中修改背景图片，搜索background</span><br><span class="line">background: url()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#修改个人头像</span><br><span class="line">在_config.butterfly.yml文件中修改个人头像，搜索avatar</span><br><span class="line">img: https://w.wallhaven.cc/full/kx/wallhaven-kx7vmm.png</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
