      <title>Linux学习环境搭建(Mac OS)</title>
      <link href="/posts/24715.html"/>
      <url>/posts/24715.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Linux环境配置-ubuntu"><a href="#Linux环境配置-ubuntu" class="headerlink" title="Linux环境配置(ubuntu)"></a>Linux环境配置(ubuntu)</h1><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><ul><li>最早接触到Linux系统是在大学做足球机器人的比赛，那个时候啥都不知道，配置的那叫一个恶心，现在重新配置，基本上还是信手拈来，无论怎么样，遇到啥就配置啥吧，以后就在这篇文章进行一些Linux环境配置的更新了</li></ul><h2 id="安装ubuntu"><a href="#安装ubuntu" class="headerlink" title="安装ubuntu"></a>安装ubuntu</h2><h3 id="安装parallels-desktop"><a href="#安装parallels-desktop" class="headerlink" title="安装parallels desktop"></a>安装parallels desktop</h3><h3 id="梯子"><a href="#梯子" class="headerlink" title="梯子"></a>梯子</h3><ul><li>虽然梯子一直是国内大家都不是很乐意提及的东西，但是一个技术人员最好还是有一个梯子，他能帮你省去很多麻烦的事情。一下的一些配置很多是建立在有梯子的基础之上的，如果没有梯子，可以考虑使用国内的镜像源</li></ul><h2 id="常见环境配置"><a href="#常见环境配置" class="headerlink" title="常见环境配置"></a>常见环境配置</h2><h3 id="更新系统软件环境"><a href="#更新系统软件环境" class="headerlink" title="更新系统软件环境"></a>更新系统软件环境</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">--打开终端</span><br><span class="line">&#x27;⌃&#x27;+&#x27;⌥&#x27;+&#x27;T&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--更新系统的的apt资源</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--软件更新(或者在图形界面点击软件更新)</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get upgrade </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">--设备重启</span><br><span class="line">reboot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="中文环境配置"><a href="#中文环境配置" class="headerlink" title="中文环境配置"></a>中文环境配置</h3><ul><li>中文语言包下载</li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%8C%85%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A41.png" alt="中文包安装步骤1"></p><ul><li><p>选择自己想要安装的语言</p><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E6%83%B3%E8%A6%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80.png" alt="选择自己想要安装的语言"></p></li><li><p>选择简体中文</p></li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E7%AE%80%E4%BD%93%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87.png" alt="选择简体中文"></p><ul><li>将中文移动到最上面一层，然后点击下面的ApplySystem-Wide,输入密码之后，重启一下即可</li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E7%A7%BB%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%80%E4%B8%8A%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%BC.png" alt="将中文移到最上面一格"></p><h3 id="输入法配置"><a href="#输入法配置" class="headerlink" title="输入法配置"></a>输入法配置</h3><ul><li>安装ibus拼音引擎</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install ibus-pinyin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>点击设置中的键盘，在输入源中添加智能拼音选项</li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%9C%A8%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%BA%90%E4%B8%AD%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%8B%BC%E9%9F%B3%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9.png" alt="在输入源中添加智能拼音选项"></p><ul><li>以上输入法就配置完成了，十分的简单～，按shift键就可以进行中英文的切换(吐槽一下ubuntu的搜狗输入法是真的难用)</li></ul><h3 id="安装git"><a href="#安装git" class="headerlink" title="安装git"></a>安装git</h3><ul><li>更新存储库</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>安装git</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudp apt install -y git </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>检查安装是否成功</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>设置用户名和email</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 设置用户名密码</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;your_name&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;email@rezhuji.com&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#验证是否生效</span><br><span class="line">git config --list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装vscode并配置环境"><a href="#安装vscode并配置环境" class="headerlink" title="安装vscode并配置环境"></a>安装vscode并配置环境</h3><ul><li>解压下载的安装包</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo dpkg -i code_1.74.3-1673284080_arm64.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>终端添加gcc和g++</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install gcc</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install g++</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>安装中文语言包</li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E5%8C%85.png" alt="安装中文语言包"></p><ul><li>安装C&#x2F;C++</li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83.png" alt="安装编译环境"></p><ul><li>安装CodeRunner</li></ul><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Coderunner.png" alt="安装Coderunner"></p><h2 id="ssh远程连接-Termius"><a href="#ssh远程连接-Termius" class="headerlink" title="ssh远程连接(Termius)"></a>ssh远程连接(Termius)</h2><h3 id="ubuntu开启ssh"><a href="#ubuntu开启ssh" class="headerlink" title="ubuntu开启ssh"></a>ubuntu开启ssh</h3><ul><li>分别安装openssh-client和openssh-server</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install openssh-client</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install openssh-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>启动服务器的ssh服务</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo service ssh start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>检查ssh服务是否启动</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ps -e | grep ssh </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5ssh%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8.png" alt="检查ssh服务是否启动"></p><ul><li>设置开机自动启动ssh服务(可选)</li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#开启开机自动启动ssh服务</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl enable ssh </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#关闭开机自动启动ssh服务</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl disable ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="开启22端口"><a href="#开启22端口" class="headerlink" title="开启22端口"></a>开启22端口</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#安装防火墙</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install ufw</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#开启防火墙</span><br><span class="line">sudo ufw enable</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#开启22端口</span><br><span class="line">sudo ufw allow 22</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#安装net-tools工具</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install net-tools</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#检查22端口是否正常打开，如果有信息，则表示22端口开启</span><br><span class="line">netstat -ntlp|grep 22</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="设置静态ip"><a href="#设置静态ip" class="headerlink" title="设置静态ip"></a>设置静态ip</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#修改网卡的配置文件(根据自己主机的网卡数量进行相应的配置)</span><br><span class="line">sudo vi /etc/netplan/00-network-manager-all.yaml</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#配置完成之后重启，并查看是否配置静态ip成功，以及22端口是否开启</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81ip.png" alt="设置静态ip"></p><ul><li>配置完静态IP之后，如果你更换了ip地址，你就得先将dhcp打开，并注释掉其他配置，之后再重新设置静态ip，否则会出现网络问题</li></ul><h3 id="Termius远程连接"><a href="#Termius远程连接" class="headerlink" title="Termius远程连接"></a>Termius远程连接</h3><p><img src="https://clh-tuchuang.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/Linux%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/termius%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE.png" alt="termius连接设置"></p><p>这里的用户名不能是ubuntu登录界面的用户名，那个是有大写的(这个天坑～)，以上就是远程ssh连接到ubuntu的步骤了，有些步骤比较繁琐，ubuntu的版本是22.04，总体上来说还是十分的简单～</p>]]></content>
      
      
